version_description: Simple yet accurate version everyone can enjoy.
Capo 5 version, closer version to original with acoustic guitar.

I tried to choose the most accurate chords possible, based on every single sound coming out of the song (bass line and background sounds). They are not so obvious, considering that the song doesn't play chords.
The chords are 100% correct and it is easy to play. It is based on the original track The Bends.
